Cabal-Version:       3.0
Name:                heap
Version:             2.0.0.0

Category:            Data Structures
Synopsis:            Binomial min-heap.
Description:
  Spine-strict binomial min-heaps, both Ord-constrained and specialized.

  See the <https://github.com/pruvisto/heap/blob/master/README.md README>
  for a brief overview of the data structures included in this package.

